main event: An unidentified object was observed on July 22, 1955, around 3:32 am in Mount, Illinois.
interesting points: The object was described as two shaped objects with various unusual characteristics.
The objects were reported to be maneuverable and appear solid.
Two photographs of the objects were taken.
The conclusion of the report was that the objects could not be identified.
The report mentions attempts to identify the objects, but it was impossible at that late date.
